						               													<description>Gold n' Grog is a press your luck pirate themed card game where players aim to collect as much treasure as they possibly can. Use Action Cards to aid your drawing power or to hinder your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gold n' Grog can be learned in less than 5 minutes.&amp;#10;To setup, all you need to do is pass out 1 cutlass card to each player, then mix the rest of the cards into a large face-down pile in the center of the table.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Turns are made up of 2 phases.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Action Phase&amp;#10;    Draw Phase&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During your Action Phase, you may play as many action cards from your hand as your pirate heart desires. For you draw phase, you may draw up to 5 cards from the draw pile, one at a time. If you find yourself without a cutlass and you run into something bad, you'll lose your draw, otherwise you may collect all the drawn cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
